The NEWS file for the SoundPanel package.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.9.3 -- 03/16/2006

This release is only to accomadate changes in the linking libraries
needed to support changes in LibRadio.  No new functionality.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.9.2 -- 02/15/2006

Added make targeets for building Slackware and SLAX packages, using
'make slack' and 'make slax', respectively.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.9.1 -- 12/01/2005

This is a bugfix release, that fixes a problem with adding new button
items with a blank 'Legend' entry.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.9.0 -- 11/10/2005
Changes:
   Added a 'Cut' item to the panel button right-click menu.

   Numerous small bugfixes -- see the 'ChangeLog' for details.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.8.1 -- 12/17/2004
Changes:
   ALSA is no longer supported.

   It is now possible to play back .mp2 and .mp3 format files if your
   ASI card supports the appropriate MPEG layer.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.4.1 -- 4/5/2004
A beta release.

     *.mp* file format playout support added for the HPI version.  The
     underlying hardware must support the appropriate MPEG format
     (e.g. an ASI6000 series adapter will be needed for *.mp3 support.

     Added a 'General' item to the 'Settings' menu, where the default
     array to load upon startup can be specified.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.2.1 -- 4/28/2003
A beta release.

     SoundPanel can now be resized.  The panel buttons will scale
     accordingly.

     Input and output level controls have been added to Sound Devices
     dialog (HPI version only).

     Miscellaneous bugfixes.  See the ChangeLog for details.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.2.1 -- 4/28/2003
A beta release.

     Fixed a missing 'defaults.h' file.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.2.0 -- 4/28/2003
A beta release.  The major highlights:

     Dynamic panels.  It's now possible to insert and delete whole
     panels from an array, thus making possible arrays of arbitrary size,
     limited only by the physical capacity of the underlying
     filesystems.

     A raft of bugfixes.  See the ChangeLog for the nitty-gritty.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.1.0 
The initial beta release.  See the README file for details.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
